text: Carneades superba is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1869. It is known from Costa Rica, Honduras, Panama and Nicaragua.BioLib.cz - Carneades superba. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1869
